<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #ffc107;
        color: #000;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
      }
      .order-details {
        background-color: white;
        padding: 15px;
        border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
      .urgency-high {
        background-color: #dc3545;
        color: white;
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
      .urgency-medium {
        background-color: #fd7e14;
        color: white;
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6c757d;
      }
      .label {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #495057;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h2>üö® Urgent Order Reminder</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <%= @user.name %>,</p>

      <% if @days_until_deadline == 1 %>
        <div class="urgency-high">
          ‚ö†Ô∏è ATTENTION: This order expires TOMORROW
        </div>
      <% else %>
        <div class="urgency-medium">
          ‚è∞ This order expires in <%= @days_until_deadline %> days
        </div>
      <% end %>

      <p>We remind you that the following urgent order is approaching its deadline:</p>

      <div class="order-details">
        <p><span class="label">Order:</span> <%= @order.order_number %></p>
        <p><span class="label">Start date:</span> <%= @order.start_date.strftime('%m/%d/%Y') %></p>
        <p><span class="label">Deadline:</span> <%= @order.deadline.strftime('%m/%d/%Y') %></p>
        <p><span class="label">Status:</span> <%= @order.status.humanize %></p>
        <p><span class="label">Days remaining:</span> <%= @days_until_deadline %></p>
      </div>

      <p>Please ensure all associated tasks are completed before the deadline.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated email generated by the Kiuey production management system.</p>
      <p>Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
